    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2014-09-17</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2015-07-08T14:00:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Teacher Tax Relief Act of 2014 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the tax deduction for the expenses of elementary and secondary school teachers, to: (1) allow an inflation adjustment to the amount of such deduction for taxable years beginning after 2013, (2) allow the deduction of professional development expenses, and (3) make such deduction permanent. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
